Package: modeltime.ensemble
Type: Package
Title: Ensemble algorithms for Modeltime Forecasting
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matt", "Dancho", email = "mdancho@business-science.io", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Business Science", role = "cph")
    )
Description: 
    Modeltime extension that implements ensemble forecasting methods including model averaging, 
    weighted averaging via penalized regression, and stacking. 
